    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a masterclass in JDM engineering, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six mated to a Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle retains its factory sequential turbocharger configuration, delivering linear power without boost leaks or shaft play. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, showcasing pristine suspension geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential. All VIN tags are present on original body panels, and the engine bay exhibits no thermal fatigue on the wiring harness or vacuum lines. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and a high-zinc oil change to protect the forged internals. This is a rare, unmolested specimen offering peak compression and exceptional mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
