      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero swirls, chips, or imperfections, while the original alloy wheels remain free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather remains supple and matte\u2014exactly as it left the factory\u2014and the interior still carries a hint of that new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at certified specialists. Complete with a full set of keys, original manuals, and a comprehensive service dossier, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
